post_text:
To assist our students with technical issues during these difficult times, the School District is providing technology support to students that have software and hardware issues. Students can access a support line at 562-602-6084 or email at pusdstudentsupport@paramount.k12.ca.us for program and software issues.

Additionally, District technology staff has set up a Chromebook technical support area in the District office (ROP Portable). Starting today, parents and students will be able to bring their District issued Chromebooks that are non-functional or having technical issues for repair or replacement at no charge. Technical services will be provided daily from 8 to 10:30 a.m. in the portable building located in the parking lot of the District office.
